A white paper released on Saturday has expounded on China's whole-process people's democracy under the leadership of the Communist Party of China (CPC). The white paper, titled "China: Democracy That Works," was released by the State Council Information Office. Whole-process people's democracy is a creation of the CPC in leading the people to pursue, develop and realize democracy, embodying the Party's innovation in advancing China's democratic theories, systems and practices, said the white paper.